    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:44.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# SET_APP_STATUS with CONFIRMED triggers code generation for apps\n\nThe app creation flow has a specific trigger point. After configuring the app document (name, document types, drag-and-drop settings), setting the status to `CONFIRMED` kicks off code generation:\n\n```typescript\naddActions({\n  documentId: appDocId,\n  actions: [{\n    type: \"SET_APP_STATUS\",\n    scope: \"global\",\n    input: { status: \"CONFIRMED\" }\n  }]\n});\n```\n\nThis creates:\n- Editor scaffolding in `editors/<app-name>/`\n- Updated `powerhouse.manifest.json` with the app entry\n\nOnly after this step can you work on the generated `editor.tsx` to customize the UI.\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[mcp workflows]]\n- [[editor patterns]]",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:44.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:44.000Z"
    }
  },
